API Endpoints
1) Method: POST
   Endpoint: /add-new-booking
   Description: Creates a new booking and stores it in the booking table

2) Method: DELETE
   Endpoint: /delete-booking
   Description: Deletes an existing booking in the booking table by checking the email and datetime of the booking in the bookings table

3) Method: GET
   Endpoint: /get-bookings
   Descriptio: Gets all the bookings in the booking table 

4) Method: PUT
   Endpoint: /edit-booking
   Description: Edits an existing booking in the bookings table
